summary: Gives Merchants, fences and caravans over 65,000 gold
descriptionHtml:
This mod gives anyone you can buy/sell things from over 65,000 gold

This is especially made for people who regularly steal/take items so they can sell them but find later that the merchant does not have enough gold.

Permissions:
Do what ever you want with it, no credit is needed as this is not original concept.

Conflicts:
This mod does not have any known conflicts, but may do if any other mods that give merchants more gold are active.
author: Harrythebeast
